18 SECTION 6. IC 21-22-6-13 IS ADDED TO THE INDIANA CODE
19 AS A NEW SECTION TO READ AS FOLLOWS [EFFECTIVE JULY
20 1, 2026]: Sec. 13. (a) On or before July 1, 2027, and each July 1
21 thereafter, Ivy Tech Community College shall provide to each
22 campus board, in a manner and form prescribed by the state board
23 of trustees, the information described in IC 21-14-15-1(1) through
24 IC 21-14-15-1(13).
25 (b) Each campus shall provide to its campus board, at each
26 regularly scheduled meeting, a performance dashboard that
27 includes:
28 (1) the annual goals established by the campus strategic plan
29 under section 15 of this chapter;
30 (2) progress toward each annual goal as of the date of the
31 report;
32 (3) a comparison of current progress to outcomes achieved for
33 the same period of the prior year; and
34 (4) an explanation of contributing factors and proposed
35 corrective actions for any goals where progress is significantly
36 below target.
37 (c) The state board of trustees shall establish a standardized
38 format for the performance dashboard described in subsection (b)
39 to ensure consistency across campuses, while permitting the
40 inclusion of campus specific metrics.
