2 JULY 1, 2026]: Sec. 3. (a) As used in this section, "management
3 performance hub" refers to the management performance hub
4 established by IC 4-3-26-8.
5 (b) Not later than July 1, 2025, and before July 1 of each year
6 thereafter, each workforce focused agency shall deliver to the
7 management performance hub a workforce related program report,
8 including any related or supporting data contemplated by the
