10 under subsection (c)(2).
11 (c) Before June 30, 2025, each workforce focused agency shall do
12 the following:
13 (1) Establish a workforce related program data governance team
14 of subject matter experts.
15 (2) Develop a common set of data elements to be used to evaluate
16 the workforce related program.
17 (3) To the extent reasonably possible, include in a contract
18 entered into or renewed after June 30, 2024, between a workforce
19 focused agency and a person conducting, operating, or
20 administering a workforce related program a provision that
21 requires the person to provide the workforce focused agency with
22 the common set of data elements developed under subdivision (2).
